title: 12/13 Fantasy Football Podcast: Tough Calls, Commish Issues, DEN-IND
description:
Aaron Rodgers is back! Now, should he be back in your lineup (1:20)? And what about Jordy  Nelson (6:10)? ... Recapping the Waiver Wire (8:53) with our thoughts on Theo Riddick, Jameis Winston and even some Kickers (12:25), then we debate Carson Wentz's 2018 value (18:00) ... Week 15 tough calls (25:41) which include Alshon Jeffery (31:31), Mike Evans (34:35) and more, plus a tough Commissioner conundrum (37:20) and a DEN-IND preview (48:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
